{"tid":1765962,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民間記者會-- 暴政矯詐冤未雪 訴求未竟誓不休","createTime":"2019-12-02T08:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T10:07:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":106,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"07608879a46954a0aa6fbd60ee0a5137f6a1bc43","tid":1765962,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:50:36.000Z","msg":"各大傳媒機構、採訪主任、編輯及記者：<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會通知<br />\n<br />\n是次記者會主題：<br />\n暴政矯詐冤未雪<br />\n訴求未竟誓不休<br />\n<br />\n區選結果塵埃落定，抗爭運動重回主線。上週末，數十萬巿民再次上街，顯示港人對公義、民主的追求及堅持。港共政權不單沒有正面回應市民的訴求，反而顛倒是非宣稱「區選舉行順利，反映了市民對暴力不滿」，更妄圖以違背市民訴求的「獨立檢討委員會」去敷衍廣大巿民及欺騙國際社會，對此民間記者會將作出回應。<br />\n <br />\n現誠邀    貴機構派員出席採訪，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年12月3日（星期二)<br />\n時間：晚上7時30分<br />\n<br />\n記者會後將設有問答環節，如有查詢可向金先生查詢。<br />\n<br />\n金先生    謹啟<br />\n2019 年 12月 2日"},{"pid":"0bf3e97547e74d36bf3eb9e0185729113ca268bb","tid":1765962,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f1d98d0cc651cce88e5e391a2bc5aac594bdb4","tid":1765962,"uid":60259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"59c868bbc359ff173144b82ae0403d72418f6bdf","tid":1765962,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6f1d98d0cc651cce88e5e391a2bc5aac594bdb4","tid":1765962,"uid":60259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"推推推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass